    "headline": "Albemarle (ALB) Q1 2026 Earnings Transcript",
    "summary": "Jerry Masters: Thank you, Meredith.  Moreover, year-to-date, we've delivered $40 million in cost and productivity improvements and remain on track to hit our full year target of $100 million to $150 million.",
    "url": "https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2026/05/07/albemarle-alb-q1-2026-earnings-transcript/",
    "source": "Motley Fool",
